column5: Big thanks to SS who dropped off the free boat this morning.  Another fine example of OFC members helping each other out.  Once I've had a chance to clean her up she'll be a fine vessel for small quiet waters.  Cheers,  Corn Nug
thats generous SS, good to hear some people still are. lets see the boat
yes he is a top notch guy...came all the way down to the niagara and took me fishing only to get skunked....super nice guy.   Hasn't contacted me since....LOL......but oh well!
Did you get out on Sunday Nug?  I was waiting for the report...  Sherriff
